text:
Oh, Kaho,
What are you looking at?
This is a photo I took before!

It's from when Natsuha-san, Cattleya, Mamemaru,
and I went to the dog park!
Would you like to see it too, Natsuha-san?
Thank you, sorry to bother you.
...Hehe, you took a lot of them.

Cattleya and Mamemaru
looked so incredibly happy!
